WEBVTT

00:00.042 --> 00:00.042
23.976

00:01.460 --> 00:03.170
Previously on
"Criminal Minds"...

00:03.378 --> 00:04.713
I lost my father...

00:05.964 --> 00:07.925
When I was 9 years old.

00:08.007 --> 00:09.051
He was shot and killed
right in front of me.

00:09.384 --> 00:10.677
Is that your daughter?
Where is she?

00:10.761 --> 00:11.678
She's with my sister.

00:11.762 --> 00:13.138
This is about you.
There's no history

00:13.222 --> 00:15.307
at your sister's place.

00:17.351 --> 00:19.478
Promise me
she'll be ok, Morgan.

00:19.520 --> 00:21.688
Do it and promise him!

00:22.731 --> 00:25.150
Ok.
Promise me, Morgan.

00:25.192 --> 00:26.527
Ok!

00:28.403 --> 00:29.821
I promise.

00:29.863 --> 00:32.198
I love you, Ellie.

