01:00.936 --> 01:03.522
Oh, my hands are numb.

01:03.564 --> 01:06.483
One more try.
You can do it.

01:06.567 --> 01:07.568
Am I close?

01:07.609 --> 01:09.319
Just keep trying.

01:09.403 --> 01:11.697
I can't, I can't.

01:11.738 --> 01:13.824
2...

01:13.907 --> 01:16.493
3...

01:16.577 --> 01:17.494
My babies...

01:17.578 --> 01:18.579
Sam and Kayla, wake up!

01:18.620 --> 01:20.581
Oh, my babies...

01:20.664 --> 01:23.250
Sammy! Kayla, wake up!

01:23.333 --> 01:24.918
He took them from me.

01:24.960 --> 01:27.171
Just keep trying.

01:27.254 --> 01:29.089
You can do it.

01:29.173 --> 01:31.133
♪ Call back anytime ♪

01:31.175 --> 01:33.468
♪ I've already had your kind ♪

01:33.552 --> 01:35.679
♪ it's a plain fact ♪

01:35.721 --> 01:39.433
♪ call me back,
call back anytime ♪

01:43.228 --> 01:45.355
Oh, no.

01:46.440 --> 01:48.192
♪ Call me anytime ♪

01:48.275 --> 01:50.152
♪ you already brought me back ♪

01:53.322 --> 01:54.615
No!

01:54.656 --> 01:55.949
You get away from her!

01:56.033 --> 01:57.451
Get away from her!

01:57.534 --> 01:59.703
Come here!
You never fought a man

01:59.786 --> 02:02.873
in your pathetic life,
you twisted psycho.

02:02.956 --> 02:04.666
No! Get out of our house!

02:04.750 --> 02:07.711
No! Please! Stop it!

02:07.753 --> 02:08.794
Please!

02:10.005 --> 02:12.341
Last night, all 4 members
of the Bennett family

02:12.424 --> 02:14.843
were killed in their home
in Council Bluffs, Iowa.

02:14.927 --> 02:17.513
Jake and Sandra Bennett
were the parents

02:17.554 --> 02:21.558
of Sammy, 11, and Kayla, 9.

02:21.642 --> 02:24.061
Agent Beeks in the Omaha
field office called me.

02:24.144 --> 02:25.854
The previous night,
the other family, the Archers,

02:25.938 --> 02:27.981
were killed just across
the state line in Nebraska.

02:28.065 --> 02:29.441
He thinks
it's the same offender.

02:29.525 --> 02:31.026
The M.O. is consistent.

02:31.109 --> 02:33.320
Both mothers died due to
severe blunt-force trauma,

02:33.362 --> 02:34.988
and the fathers suffered
multiple stab wounds.

02:35.072 --> 02:37.324
The children
were all strangled.

02:37.366 --> 02:39.326
Violence only
in the kids' rooms,

02:39.368 --> 02:41.578
but no sexual abuse
on any of the children.

02:41.662 --> 02:42.955
That's odd.

02:42.996 --> 02:44.957
Odd comes up right now,

02:44.998 --> 02:47.668
because the Bennett father
was not just stabbed,

02:47.751 --> 02:49.670
he was also...

02:49.711 --> 02:51.171
And those pictures
are in your personal files

02:51.213 --> 02:53.382
because I didn't think
they needed the help of 1080p.

02:53.465 --> 02:58.011
His chest was opened,
organs disturbed, intestines removed.

02:58.053 --> 03:00.013
That's awesome.
Could we please leave the gross part

03:00.055 --> 03:01.014
of the conversation
for the plane?

03:01.056 --> 03:02.641
The father of the Archer family

03:02.683 --> 03:04.977
had multiple stab wounds
but no dissection.

03:05.018 --> 03:08.730
So he went from piquerism
to this overnight?

03:08.814 --> 03:11.191
2 families in 2 days.
He's on a spree.

03:11.233 --> 03:12.776
Wheels up in 30.

03:19.908 --> 03:21.451
Hey, Morgan.

03:31.587 --> 03:34.256
Ellie, how did you get past
airport security?

03:34.339 --> 03:37.342
I stayed real close
to this family.

03:37.384 --> 03:38.844
Nobody asked.

03:38.886 --> 03:41.638
If they had, I would have
said I was 12,

03:41.722 --> 03:43.307
'cause you can fly by yourself.

03:43.390 --> 03:45.684
This is not all right.

03:45.726 --> 03:47.895
You can't just run away
like this.

03:47.936 --> 03:51.523
But that house is awful.

03:51.565 --> 03:55.402
This older boy tries
to watch me in the shower.

04:00.407 --> 04:02.576
Hey. It's way early in L.A.

04:02.618 --> 04:04.453
I left a message
with Child Protective Services,

04:04.536 --> 04:05.621
but I haven't heard...

04:05.704 --> 04:07.623
you can't send me back there.

04:07.664 --> 04:11.251
Ellie, you're a missing kid.

04:11.293 --> 04:14.129
We have to let them
know you're safe.

04:14.213 --> 04:16.839
I didn't know where else to go.

04:18.050 --> 04:19.468
I know.

04:21.053 --> 04:23.972
Listen, this is one of
my very good friends, Penelope.

04:24.056 --> 04:25.807
She's going to look
after you while I'm gone.

04:25.891 --> 04:28.310
Hi, honey.

04:28.393 --> 04:31.563
Ellie, I'll come back
as soon as I can.

04:36.568 --> 04:37.778
Come on, Ellie.

04:40.072 --> 04:40.989
Go ahead.

04:41.073 --> 04:43.659
It's ok.

04:45.327 --> 04:46.537
Come on, Ellie.

04:48.121 --> 04:49.748
Have you ever been
in a lair before?

04:49.790 --> 04:51.208
You'll like it.

04:55.420 --> 04:57.256
What are you gonna do?

04:57.297 --> 04:59.550
I don't know.

